								</path>
							</svg> Tech Stack</span>
						<h2 class="mt-3 text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">Built on a <span
								class="text-gradient">battle-tested</span> foundation.</h2>
						<p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground max-w-lg">Expo + React Native deliver native performance
							across iOS and Android, while Supabase handles authentication and data with a clean
							developer experience.</p>
						<div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-w-md">
							<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div
									class="h-9 w-9 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card flex items-center justify-center">
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
										fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"
										stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-smartphone h-4 w-4 text-primary"
										aria-hidden="true">
										<rect width="14" height="20" x="5" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
										<path d="M12 18h.01"></path>
									</svg>
